04f8h8u7qjcrq with ss as ( select /*+ MATERIALIZE */ to_char(hss.end_interval_time - 10*1/1440, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24') hourly_end_interval_time, max(hss.snap_id) max_snap, to_char(SUM(hss.interval_seconds), 99999999) seconds from ( select min(hss2.instance_number) instance_number, hss2.snap_id, min(hss1.snap_id) prev_snap_id, min(hss2.begin_interval_time) begin_interval_time, max(hss2.end_interval_time) end_interval_time, max(to_char(hss2.end_interval_time, 'SSSSS') - to_char(hss2.begin_interval_time, 'SSSSS') + 86400 * (to_char(hss2.end_interval_time, 'J') - to_char(hss2.begin_interval_time, 'J'))) interval_seconds, min(decode(hss2.startup_time, hss1.startup_time, 'NO', 'YES')) restart from dba_hist_snapshot hss1, dba_hist_snapshot hss2 where hss2.dbid = ( select dbid from v$database ) and hss1.dbid (+) = hss2.dbid and hss1.instance_number (+) = hss2.instance_number and hss1.snap_id (+) = hss2.snap_id - 1 and hss2.snap_id between :A0 and :A1 group by hss2.snap_id order by hss2.snap_i d ) hss group by to_char(hss.end_interval_time - 10*1/1440, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24') ), sum_space as ( select /*+ MATERIALIZE */ dh.snap_id, round(sum(((dh.tablespace_size - dh.tablespace_usedsize) * decode(dt.block_size, null, 8192, dt.block_size)) / (1024 * 1024))) freesize_mb, round(sum((dh.tablespace_usedsize * decode(dt.block_size, null, 8192, dt.block_size)) / (1024 * 1024))) usedsize_mb, round(sum((dh.tablespace_maxsize * decode(dt.block_size, null, 8192, dt.block_size)) / (1024 * 1024))) maxsize_mb from dba_hist_tbspc_space_usage dh, dba_tablespaces dt, v$tablespace vt where dh.snap_id between :A2 and :A3 and dh.tablespace_id = vt.ts#(+) and vt.name = dt.tablespace_name and dh.dbid = ( select dbid from v$database ) group by dh.snap_id ) select hourly_end_interval_time, max_snap, seconds, freesize_mb, usedsize_mb, maxsize_mb, ( usedsize_mb - lag( usedsize_mb) over (order by max_snap)) delta_mb from ss, sum_space where sum_space.snap_id = ss.max_snap order by ss.max_snap

bccq8ux14yj7d WITH SNAPSHOTS AS ( SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */ DBID, INSTANCE_NUMBER, SNAP_ID, PREV_SNAP_ID, MIN_SNAP_ID, BEGIN_INTERVAL_TIME, END_INTERVAL_TIME, INTERVAL_SECONDS, SUM(INTERVAL_SECONDS) OVER () TOTAL_SECONDS, RESTART FROM ( SELECT HSS2.DBID, HSS2.INSTANCE_NUMBER, HSS2.SNAP_ID, HSS1.SNAP_ID PREV_SNAP_ID, MIN(HSS2.SNAP_ID) OVER (PARTITION BY HSS2.INSTANCE_NUMBER) MIN_SNAP_ID, HSS2.BEGIN_INTERVAL_TIME, HSS2.END_INTERVAL_TIME, TO_CHAR(HSS2.END_INTERVAL_TIME, 'SSSSS') - TO_CHAR(HSS2.BEGIN_INTERVAL_TIME, 'SSSSS') + 86400 * (TO_CHAR(HSS2.END_INTERVAL_TIME, 'J') - TO_CHAR(HSS2.BEGIN_INTERVAL_TIME, 'J')) INTERVAL_SECONDS, DECODE(HSS2.STARTUP_TIME, HSS1.STARTUP_TIME, 'NO', 'YES') RESTART FROM DBA_HIST_SNAPSHOT HSS1, DBA_HIST_SNAPSHOT HSS2 WHERE HSS2.DBID = ( SELECT DBID FROM V$DATABASE ) AND HSS1.DBID (+) = HSS2.DBID AND HSS1.INSTANCE_NUMBER (+) = HSS2.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HSS1.SNAP_ID (+) = HSS2.SNAP_ID - 1 AND HSS2.SNAP_ID BETWEEN :A0 AND :A1 ORDER BY HSS2.SNAP_ID ) ) SE LECT hourly_end_interval_time, INSTANCE_NUMBER, MAX(SNAP_ID) SNAP_ID, SUM(SECONDS) SECONDS, SUM(NO_DOWNGRADE) NO_DOWNGRADE, SUM(DG_1_25_PCT) DG_1_25_PCT, SUM(DG_25_50_PCT) DG_25_50_PCT, SUM(DG_50_75_PCT) DG_50_75_PCT, SUM(DG_75_99_PCT) DG_75_99_PCT, SUM(DG_SERIAL) DG_SERIAL FROM ( SELECT TO_CHAR(ss.end_interval_time - 10*1/1440, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24') hourly_end_interval_time, SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER, SS.SNAP_ID, SS.BEGIN_INTERVAL_TIME, SS.INTERVAL_SECONDS SECONDS, DECODE(SS.RESTART, 'YES', HSY1.VALUE, HSY1.VALUE - LAG(HSY1.VALUE, 1) OVER (partition by ss.instance_number ORDER BY SS.SNAP_ID)) NO_DOWNGRADE, DECODE(SS.RESTART, 'YES', HSY2.VALUE, HSY2.VALUE - LAG(HSY2.VALUE, 1) OVER (partition by ss.instance_number ORDER BY SS.SNAP_ID)) DG_1_25_PCT, DECODE(SS.RESTART, 'YES', HSY3.VALUE, HSY3.VALUE - LAG(HSY3.VALUE, 1) OVER (partition by ss.instance_number ORDER BY SS.SNAP_ID)) DG_25_50_PCT, DECODE(SS.RESTART, 'YES', HSY4.VALUE, HSY4.VALUE - LAG(HSY4.VALUE, 1) OVER (partition by ss.instance_number ORDER BY SS.SNAP_ID)) DG_50_75_PCT, DECODE(SS.RESTART, 'YES', HSY5.VALUE, HSY5.VALUE - LAG(HSY5.VALUE, 1) OVER (partition by ss.instance_number ORDER BY SS.SNAP_ID)) DG_75_99_PCT, DECODE(SS.RESTART, 'YES', HSY6.VALUE, HSY6.VALUE - LAG(HSY6.VALUE, 1) OVER (partition by ss.instance_number ORDER BY SS.SNAP_ID)) DG_SERIAL, SS.PREV_SNAP_ID, SS.MIN_SNAP_ID FROM SNAPSHOTS SS, DBA_HIST_SYSSTAT HSY1, DBA_HIST_SYSSTAT HSY2, DBA_HIST_SYSSTAT HSY3, DBA_HIST_SYSSTAT HSY4, DBA_HIST_SYSSTAT HSY5, DBA_HIST_SYSSTAT HSY6 WHERE HSY1.DBID = SS.DBID AND HSY2.DBID = SS.DBID AND HSY3.DBID = SS.DBID AND HSY4.DBID = SS.DBID AND HSY5.DBID = SS.DBID AND HSY6.DBID = SS.DBID AND HSY1.INSTANCE_NUMBER = SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HSY2.INSTANCE_NUMBER = SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HSY3.INSTANCE_NUMBER = SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HSY4.INSTANCE_NUMBER = SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HSY5.INSTANCE_NUMBER = SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HSY6.INSTANCE_NUMBER = SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HSY1.SNAP_ID = SS.SNAP_ID AND HSY2.SNAP_ID = SS.SNAP_ID AND HSY3.SNAP_ID = SS.SNAP_ID AND HSY4.SNAP_ID = SS.SNAP_ID AND HSY5.SNAP_ID = SS.SNAP_ID AND HSY6.SNAP_ID = SS.SNAP_ID AND HSY1.STAT_NAME = 'Parallel operations not downgraded' AND HSY2.STAT_NAME = 'Parallel operations downgraded 1 to 25 pct' AND HSY3.STAT_NAME = 'Parallel operations downgraded 25 to 50 pct' AND HSY4.STAT_NAME = 'Parallel operations downgraded 50 to 75 pct' AND HSY5.STAT_NAME = 'Parallel operations downgraded 75 to 99 pct' AND HSY6.STAT_NAME = 'Parallel operations downgraded to serial' ) WHERE SNAP_ID != MIN_SNAP_ID GROUP BY hourly_end_interval_time, INSTANCE_NUMBER ORDER by SNAP_ID, INSTANCE_NUMBER

cr4vgj53ww165 WITH SNAPSHOTS AS ( SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */ DBID, INSTANCE_NUMBER, SNAP_ID, PREV_SNAP_ID, MIN_SNAP_ID, BEGIN_INTERVAL_TIME, END_INTERVAL_TIME, INTERVAL_SECONDS, SUM(INTERVAL_SECONDS) OVER () TOTAL_SECONDS, RESTART FROM ( SELECT HSS2.DBID, HSS2.INSTANCE_NUMBER, HSS2.SNAP_ID, HSS1.SNAP_ID PREV_SNAP_ID, MIN(HSS2.SNAP_ID) OVER (PARTITION BY HSS2.INSTANCE_NUMBER) MIN_SNAP_ID, HSS2.BEGIN_INTERVAL_TIME, HSS2.END_INTERVAL_TIME, TO_CHAR(HSS2.END_INTERVAL_TIME, 'SSSSS') - TO_CHAR(HSS2.BEGIN_INTERVAL_TIME, 'SSSSS') + 86400 * (TO_CHAR(HSS2.END_INTERVAL_TIME, 'J') - TO_CHAR(HSS2.BEGIN_INTERVAL_TIME, 'J')) INTERVAL_SECONDS, DECODE(HSS2.STARTUP_TIME, HSS1.STARTUP_TIME, 'NO', 'YES') RESTART FROM DBA_HIST_SNAPSHOT HSS1, DBA_HIST_SNAPSHOT HSS2 WHERE HSS2.DBID = ( SELECT DBID FROM V$DATABASE ) AND HSS1.DBID (+) = HSS2.DBID AND HSS1.INSTANCE_NUMBER (+) = HSS2.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HSS1.SNAP_ID (+) = HSS2.SNAP_ID - 1 AND HSS2.SNAP_ID BETWEEN :A0 AND :A1 ORDER BY HSS2.SNAP_ID ) ) SE LECT hourly_end_interval_time, INSTANCE_NUMBER, MAX(SNAP_ID) SNAP_ID, SUM(SECONDS) SECONDS, SUM(TIME_MODEL_TOTAL_S) TIME_MODEL_TOTAL_S, SUM(SYSSTAT_TOTAL_S) SYSSTAT_TOTAL_S, SUM(SYSSTAT_RECURSIVE_S) SYSSTAT_RECURSIVE_S, SUM(SYSSTAT_PARSE_S) SYSSTAT_PARSE_S FROM ( SELECT TO_CHAR(ss.end_interval_time - 10*1/1440, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24') hourly_end_interval_time, SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER, SS.SNAP_ID, SS.BEGIN_INTERVAL_TIME, SS.INTERVAL_SECONDS SECONDS, DECODE(SS.RESTART, 'YES', HST.VALUE, HST.VALUE - LAG(HST.VALUE, 1) OVER (partition by ss.instance_number ORDER BY SS.SNAP_ID)) / 1000000 TIME_MODEL_TOTAL_S, DECODE(SS.RESTART, 'YES', HSY1.VALUE, HSY1.VALUE - LAG(HSY1.VALUE, 1) OVER (partition by ss.instance_number ORDER BY SS.SNAP_ID)) / 100 SYSSTAT_TOTAL_S, DECODE(SS.RESTART, 'YES', HSY2.VALUE, HSY2.VALUE - LAG(HSY2.VALUE, 1) OVER (partition by ss.instance_number ORDER BY SS.SNAP_ID)) / 100 SYSSTAT_RECURSIVE_S, DECODE(SS.RESTART, 'YES', HSY3.VALUE, HSY3.VALUE - LAG(HSY3 .VALUE, 1) OVER (partition by ss.instance_number ORDER BY SS.SNAP_ID)) / 100 SYSSTAT_PARSE_S, SS.PREV_SNAP_ID, SS.MIN_SNAP_ID FROM SNAPSHOTS SS, DBA_HIST_SYSSTAT HSY1, DBA_HIST_SYSSTAT HSY2, DBA_HIST_SYSSTAT HSY3, DBA_HIST_SYS_TIME_MODEL HST WHERE HSY1.DBID = SS.DBID AND HSY2.DBID = SS.DBID AND HSY3.DBID = SS.DBID AND HST.DBID = SS.DBID AND HSY1.INSTANCE_NUMBER = SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HSY2.INSTANCE_NUMBER = SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HSY3.INSTANCE_NUMBER = SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HST.INSTANCE_NUMBER = SS.INSTANCE_NUMBER AND HSY1.SNAP_ID = SS.SNAP_ID AND HSY2.SNAP_ID = SS.SNAP_ID AND HSY3.SNAP_ID = SS.SNAP_ID AND HST.SNAP_ID = SS.SNAP_ID AND HSY1.STAT_NAME = 'CPU used by this session' AND HSY2.STAT_NAME = 'recursive cpu usage' AND HSY3.STAT_NAME = 'parse time cpu' AND HST.STAT_NAME = 'DB CPU' ) WHERE SNAP_ID != MIN_SNAP_ID GROUP BY hourly_end_interval_time, INSTANCE_NUMBER ORDER by SNAP_ID, INSTANCE_NUMBER

csw9a6xrn2y4v SELECT T.TABLESPACE_NAME AS NAME, T.STATUS, CASE (TS.AUTOEXTENSIBLE) WHEN 1 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS AUTOEXTENSIBLE, NVL(TS.MAXBYTES, 0) AS TOTAL, NVL(TS.USED, 0) AS USED, NVL(TS.FREE_TOTAL, 0) AS FREE, ROUND(NVL(TS.FREE_TOTAL, 0) / NVL(TS.MAXBYTES, 1) * 100, 2) AS FREEPERCENT, NVL(TS.FILE_COUNT, 0) AS FILE_COUNT FROM (SELECT TS.*, TS.BYTES - NVL(FREE.BYTES, 0) AS USED, TS.MAXBYTES - TS.BYTES + NVL(FREE.BYTES, 0) AS FREE_TOTAL, NVL(FREE.BYTES, 0) AS FREE_ALLOCATED FROM (SELECT NVL(TABLESPACE_NAME, 'UNKNOWN') AS TABLESPACE_NAME, MAX(AUTOEXTENSIBLE) AS AUTOEXTENSIBLE, SUM(MAXBYTES) AS MAXBYTES, SUM(BYTES) AS BYTES, COUNT(ID) AS FILE_COUNT FROM (SELECT FILE_ID AS ID, TABLESPACE_NAME, CASE (AUTOEXTENSIBLE) WHEN 'YES' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS AUTOEXTENSIBLE, CASE (AUTOEXTENSIBLE) WHEN 'YES' THEN NVL(MAXBYTES, 0) ELSE NVL(BYTES, 0) END AS "MAXBYTES", BYTES AS BYTES FROM DBA_DATA_FILES) GROUP BY TABLESPACE_NAME) TS, (SELECT NVL(TABLESPACE_NAME, 'UNKNOWN') AS TABLESPACE_NAME, SUM(BYTES) AS BYTES FROM DBA_FREE_SPACE GROUP BY TABLESPACE_NAME ) FREE WHERE FREE.TABLESPACE_NAME(+) = TS.TABLESPACE_NAME) TS, DBA_TABLESPACES T WHERE T.TABLESPACE_NAME = TS.TABLESPACE_NAME(+) ORDER BY NAME
